scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, April!

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Hi, dad!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Why do you keep climbing up here? You're too old forthis.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: These silly tricks are for kids.

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: It's perfectly safe; I've seen you jump down fromhere all the time.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: Hey, it takes a lot of practice to do that...

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Besides, I can see really far from up here!

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: That guy over there is creeping me out though;he looks like he's just waiting for something.

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: What guy?!?

scenes.name: April
scenes.text: Over there!

scenes.name: Turner
scenes.text: I'll go see what he's up to.

scenes.name: Sven##
scenes.text: Hi, stranger. I'm sorry, but for your own good,you should leave as soon as possible.

scenes.name: Garett####
scenes.text: Too late. I mustn't spread the disease...

scenes.name: Sven####
scenes.text: Why did you come?

scenes.name: Garett
scenes.text: New master ceremony...I was a little early. Unfortunately.

scenes.name: Garett
scenes.text: You should leave... Use the gate...

scenes.name: Feng##
scenes.text: Welcome back, Sven.

scenes.name: Feng###
scenes.text:
Those of us who have not fled south have gathered
at the temples. We'll act separately to counteract
treason.

scenes.name: Sven###
scenes.text: The grass here has already been poisoned...

scenes.name: Feng###
scenes.text:
We're leaving. Each of us will go on their way,
spread all over the country, to strike, and hide.

scenes.name: Feng##
scenes.text:
For them it is a foreign land. We know every cave
and tree hole.

scenes.name: Feng###
scenes.text:
I've set up secret meetings every fortnight. Your
first one is with Garett at the old fort. Then
Earl in the west clearing.

scenes.name: Sven##
scenes.text: Duly noted.

scenes.name: Sven##
scenes.text: Lenore?

scenes.name: Lenore
scenes.text: Ah...

scenes.name: Lenore
scenes.text: Poison...

scenes.name: Sven##
scenes.text: Poison?

scenes.name: Sven##
scenes.text: Hey Silb.

scenes.name: Silb###
scenes.text: Welcome back. I'll be the one to guard the temple.

scenes.name: Sven##
scenes.text: But you're still an apprentice. Are you up to it?

scenes.name: Silb###
scenes.text:
There's little choice. You may have noticed most
of us are dying here.

scenes.name: Silb###
scenes.text:
You should wish me luck. We'll need the temple
for the passing ceremony of your mastery.

scenes.name: Sven##
scenes.text: There may soon be no temple anymore. That titleis outliving its meaning.

scenes.name: Silb###
scenes.text: It will still mean something to your foes. Notmany people can cross the Great Desert and comeback through the Sand Fortress.
